measurements.description: One flat flower on one 20-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal broad, white, overlaid green basally, heavy burgundy spots coalescing at midline, white margin; synsepal white, light green centrally, spotted burgundy, more heavily centrally; petals deep burgundy, yellow picotee; pouch deep burgundy, yellow top edge; staminode pale yellow, flushed burgundy, deep yellow centrally; substance firm; texture glossy.
